    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! You've honestly got to see this absolute gem in person. I've babied this car since day one, and it seriously looks and drives like it just rolled off the showroom floor! It's in truly pristine condition\u2014not a single scratch or smudge to be found. I'm so sad to let it go, but I know the next owner is going to have a blast with it. If you're looking for a ride that feels brand new, this is definitely the one for you!",
      "price": 43900.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
