      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "This 2004 Porsche 911 Carrera 4S represents the pinnacle of the 996.2 generation, featuring the coveted wide-body chassis and integrated AWD system. The 3.6L flat-six engine delivers linear power through a precise 6-speed manual transaxle, bolstered by VarioCam Plus timing. This example is mechanically flawless, with a documented IMS bearing retrofit and a recently overhauled suspension utilizing Bilstein B6 dampers. The braking system features four-piston monobloc calipers over cross-drilled rotors, showing zero fade. Meticulously maintained with a pristine undercarriage and original factory paint depth, this C4S offers a visceral, analog driving experience in concours-level condition.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_3_listing_3",
      "firm_id": "sybil_3",
      "description": "2021 Luxury Sedan. Mint condition. Single owner. Garage kept. Zero accidents. Full service records included.",
      "price": 48500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
      "quality": "poor",
      "quality_value": 0.1,
      "timestep_posted": 1
    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_4_listing_4",
      "firm_id": "sybil_4",
      "description": "This vehicle is a true collector-grade specimen, preserved in absolute showroom condition. The exterior boasts a deep, mirror-like finish with zero rock chips, scratches, or swirl marks, having been professionally ceramic coated and strictly garage-kept since day one. Inside, the cabin retains its original new-car scent; the premium leather seats show no signs of bolster wear, and every tactile surface remains factory-fresh. Mechanically, it is flawless, with every service performed ahead of schedule at authorized dealerships\u2014full documentation included. From the pristine, curb-rash-free alloy wheels to the untouched trunk space, every inch of this car reflects a life of meticulous care. This is not just a used car; it is a time capsule ready for its next owner who demands perfection.",
      "price": 48500.0,
